OL,5, The government is being urged to throw 
OL,6, small and medium-sized businesses a    
OL,7, #9.6bn lifeline to save them from      
OL,8, soaring energy bills.                  
OL,10,FThe Liberal Democrats say firms should 
OL,11,Fbe given grants of up to #50,000 for   
OL,12,Fone year to prevent the UK's High      
OL,13,FStreets turning into "ghost towns".    
OL,15,FMany businesses - which are not covered
OL,16,Fby the household price cap - are facing
OL,17,Fhuge increases to renew contracts.     
OL,19,FThe Lib Dems say their scheme could be 
OL,20,Fpaid for by raising taxes on banks.    
